This is an independent, clean-room reimplementation. The on-screen keyboard
core, widget view, QML components, layout schema, theming API, and
translations in this repository were designed and written from scratch for
this project. No source code, build files, or bundled assets from the
original GPLv3-licensed QKeyboardWidget project (Mihaylov93/QKeyboardWidget)
are included; only the general product concept (a JSON-driven on-screen
keyboard widget for Qt) was carried over.
